data.description: Enjoy the benefits of county taxes only with this exquisite home situated in a tranquil neighborhood. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths, including a substantial bonus room, there is no shortage of space in this home. The downstairs primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroom with a shower spacious enough to accommodate a small village. Unwind by the fireplace in the expansive outdoor sunroom, ideal for hosting and relaxation just in time for the holidays. Your dream home awaits!
